of the things that you really want is for people to use your stuff, right? That's how

00:13:02.479 --> 00:13:07.679
you get tenure. That's how, you know, you get recognition in your field. And if no one

00:13:07.679 --> 00:13:12.400
knows how to use what you're giving, no one's going to use it, right? And so vignettes are

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:18.159
a really great way to do that, kind of a nice real world example of using your package.

00:13:18.159 --> 00:13:21.599
And then one of the nice things about this is that for people, if you're like me, and

00:13:21.599 --> 00:13:26.760
you don't actually like sitting down and writing academic papers, this can trick you into writing

