So with any package or any kind of method research product, there's, you know, you need

00:14:47.239 --> 00:14:53.159
to know what you need to do to use it. And so in this package, you need really, I think,

00:14:53.159 --> 00:14:57.719
a class of two things, two classes of things for what you need. One is data. So you need

00:14:57.719 --> 00:15:01.520
data that can be represented as nodes and edges between those nodes, also known as graph

