social networks. We don't currently support nondiscrete edges. And that's just because,

00:15:28.719 --> 00:15:32.880
as you saw, the distribution that we're using is the Poisson distribution, which is a discrete

00:15:32.880 --> 00:15:38.119
distribution. There are ways to extend it to nondiscrete edges, but we have not gotten

